### Homarv3 API Tests
### Make sure the server is running on http://localhost:8000

### Root endpoint - Get API information
GET http://localhost:8000/

### Health check endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Interact endpoint - With user ID
POST http://localhost:8000/interact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Zrób listę zakupów na dzisiaj z podzadaniami: marchew, keczup, makaron",
  "user_id": "user123"
}

### Home Assistant MCP Server SSE
GET http://192.168.50.30:8123/mcp_server/sse
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv HOME_ASSISTANT_TOKEN}}
